OL,3,CBBC launches investigation into
OL,4,CStrictly stars' 'cocaine use'
OL,6,FThe BBC has launched an investigation
OL,7,Finto alleged cocaine use by two of the
OL,8,Fstars of Strictly Come Dancing.
OL,10,FReports in The Sun allege their drug
OL,11,Fuse was discussed on the BBC dancing
OL,12,Fshow, and said that the corporation
OL,13,Fhad appointed law firm Pinsent Masons
OL,14,Fto lead the investigation.
