OL,6,F"We would always encourage people to
OL,7,Fspeak to us if they have concerns. It
OL,8,Fwould not be appropriate for us to
OL,9,Fcomment further."
OL,11,Fit is understood that the BBC often
OL,12,Fappoints external law firms to help it
OL,13,Flead investigations, while reporting
OL,14,Fback to an internal team.
OL,16,FThe cast members involved in the
OL,17,Finvestigation were not named by The
OL,18,FSun.
