OL,3,CBBC launches investigation into
OL,4,CStrictly stars' 'cocaine use'
OL,6,FIt comes after the BBC launched a
OL,7,Freview into Strictly in 2024 that
OL,8,Flooked into allegations of bullying
OL,9,Fand harassment against former
OL,10,Fprofessional dancer Giovanni Pernice,
OL,11,Fmade by his former dance partner
OL,12,FAmanda Abbington.
OL,14,FThe corporation upheld some, but not
OL,15,Fall, of the complaints made ` and
OL,16,Fintroduced a series of new measures
OL,17,Faimed at improving welfare.
OL,19,FThis included the introduction of a
OL,20,Fchaperone who is present "at all
OL,21,Ftimes" during training room rehearsals.
